Then who did you date?

1112
01:23:53,945 --> 01:23:54,985
Nut,

1113
01:23:55,065 --> 01:23:57,345
whatever makes you unhappy,

1114
01:23:57,425 --> 01:23:58,545
don't think about it.

1115
01:23:58,624 --> 01:24:00,105
Don't obsess over it.

1116
01:24:02,585 --> 01:24:04,065
Look ahead,

1117
01:24:04,704 --> 01:24:06,185
look around you,

1118
01:24:06,865 --> 01:24:08,704
and open up your heart.

1119
01:24:09,265 --> 01:24:11,545
It might make you happier.

1120
01:24:12,465 --> 01:24:13,664
What are you saying?

1121
01:24:14,465 --> 01:24:15,744
You'll find me a boyfriend?

1122
01:24:17,704 --> 01:24:20,025
Well, the best way
to get over your old love

1123
01:24:20,545 --> 01:24:22,105
is to find a new one, right?

1124
01:24:23,704 --> 01:24:24,905
If you're happy,

1125
01:24:25,385 --> 01:24:27,945
those romantic scenes
you're struggling with

1126
01:24:28,664 --> 01:24:30,065
will come to you naturally.

1127
01:24:32,784 --> 01:24:34,105
That's easier said than done.

1128
01:24:34,905 --> 01:24:36,624
I've been looking,

1129
01:24:36,704 --> 01:24:38,185
but I haven't found anyone.

1130
01:24:38,265 --> 01:24:39,465
You know that.

1131
01:24:41,465 --> 01:24:42,865
Shall I find someone for you?

1132
01:24:42,945 --> 01:24:43,905
It's easy.

1133
01:24:43,985 --> 01:24:45,545
Two people you know,

1134
01:24:45,624 --> 01:24:47,025
they're crazy about you.

1135
01:24:48,824 --> 01:24:50,425
It's either Prib or Tofu.

1136
01:24:53,305 --> 01:24:55,105
I'm sorry, Prib.

1137
01:24:55,824 --> 01:24:57,784
You cooked for Nut,

1138
01:24:57,865 --> 01:24:59,624
but I made him angry,

1139
01:25:00,385 --> 01:25:01,704
so…

1140
01:25:02,945 --> 01:25:04,305
It's fine.

1141
01:25:05,345 --> 01:25:06,624
It's not your fault.

1142
01:25:07,305 --> 01:25:08,545
Not Nut's fault either.

1143
01:25:09,505 --> 01:25:10,865
It was an accident.

1144
01:25:10,945 --> 01:25:12,345
I understand.

1145
01:25:13,145 --> 01:25:14,585
I can cook again another time.

1146
01:25:29,145 --> 01:25:31,145
It's okay. I'll clean it up.

1147
01:25:37,945 --> 01:25:39,265
By the way,

1148
01:25:39,345 --> 01:25:41,664
how come Nut's work
has to be revised so much?

1149
01:25:42,505 --> 01:25:43,545
Do you know?

1150
01:25:44,824 --> 01:25:48,025
Juea said his romantic scenes
still aren't good enough.

1151
01:25:48,905 --> 01:25:51,225
I guess his past is pretty bitter.

1152
01:25:53,185 --> 01:25:54,465
What does his past

1153
01:25:55,065 --> 01:25:56,704
have to do with his work?

1154
01:25:56,784 --> 01:25:58,664
He's writing about his life.

1155
01:25:59,145 --> 01:26:00,985
Even if it's a little sad,

1156
01:26:01,784 --> 01:26:02,704
that's okay,

1157
01:26:02,784 --> 01:26:05,985
because I'll add sweetness to his life,

1158
01:26:07,065 --> 01:26:08,865
and then things will go well.

1159
01:26:17,784 --> 01:26:19,065
I'm sorry, Prib.

1160
01:26:20,784 --> 01:26:21,985
You too, Tofu.

1161
01:26:23,265 --> 01:26:24,624
Sorry for losing my temper.

1162
01:26:26,265 --> 01:26:27,744
It's okay, Nut.

1163
01:26:27,824 --> 01:26:29,905
I understand everything.

1164
01:26:29,985 --> 01:26:32,345
I'll make you fried pork another time.

1165
01:26:32,425 --> 01:26:34,824
You can look forward to that.

1166
01:26:40,385 --> 01:26:41,465
Something wrong, Gen?

1167
01:26:41,945 --> 01:26:43,225
I have an emergency.

1168
01:26:43,305 --> 01:26:45,465
Sorry, Prib. Go home by yourself.

1169
01:26:45,545 --> 01:26:46,624
What?

1170
01:26:54,545 --> 01:26:55,945
Nut.

1171
01:26:59,545 --> 01:27:00,824
All right,

1172
01:27:02,225 --> 01:27:03,425
I'll call you a taxi.

1173
01:27:19,985 --> 01:27:21,385
You're doing this again, Mom!

1174
01:27:23,265 --> 01:27:24,784
When will you understand

1175
01:27:25,345 --> 01:27:27,664
that going into someone's room
without permission

1176
01:27:27,744 --> 01:27:29,545
is an invasion of privacy?

1177
01:27:43,505 --> 01:27:44,624
What are you doing?

1178
01:27:47,505 --> 01:27:49,305
I just want to know what you wrote.

1179
01:27:52,185 --> 01:27:54,065
What I write is my business.

1180
01:28:09,864 --> 01:28:11,425
NEXT EPISODE

1181
01:28:11,505 --> 01:28:12,864
Mister.

1182
01:28:13,465 --> 01:28:14,704
Song!

1183
01:28:17,265 --> 01:28:19,185
I didn't mean to cause any trouble.

1184
01:28:19,265 --> 01:28:21,225
But you chose to get involved.

1185
01:28:21,305 --> 01:28:24,345
I hope you can put an end
to this problem soon

1186
01:28:24,425 --> 01:28:26,145
without affecting our work.

1187
01:28:27,585 --> 01:28:29,145
Mrs. Na!

1188
01:28:33,465 --> 01:28:34,945
Are you happy, Nut?

1189
01:28:38,425 --> 01:28:39,385
Woo-hoo!

1190
01:28:39,864 --> 01:28:41,265
Your lips…

1191
01:28:43,704 --> 01:28:45,465
are sweet and soft like jelly.

1192
01:28:45,545 --> 01:28:47,265
Why do you sound like…

1193
01:28:48,105 --> 01:28:49,105
Who the hell are you?

1194
01:28:51,025 --> 01:28:52,465
Why are you doing this?

1195
01:28:53,025 --> 01:28:54,744
What do you want from me?

1196
